Interface ISmartSortedSet<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>

All Superinterfaces:
java.util.Collection<E>, ISmartCollection<E>, ISmartSet<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>, java.util.Set<E>, java.util.SortedSet<E>
public interface ISmartSortedSet<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>
extends java.util.SortedSet<E>, ISmartSet<E>

Specifies the operations of SmartSortedSets. SmartSortedSets are compatible with the standard SortedSet interface, but add some functionality to them. They are implemented as simple decorators (see Gang of Four).
